                (BASEL 2 BRF.EXP. 11.II.17XII–)
                
                Maestro
                <lb/><persName key="E0300017">Ferruccio Busoni</persName>
                <lb/><placeName key="E0500189">Scheuchzerstr. 36</placeName>
                <lb/><placeName key="E0500132">Zürich</placeName>.
                
                <note type="stamp" place="…" resp="#dsb_st_red">
                    <stamp rend="round border align(center) small">Deutsche
                        <lb/>Staatsbibliothek
                        <lb/><placeName key="E0500029"><hi rend="spaced-out">Berlin</hi></placeName>
                    </stamp>
                </note>
                
                <note type="shelfmark" place="…" resp="#archive">Mus.Nachl. F. Busoni B II, 2284</note>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
                
                <opener><salute rend="align(right)">Verehrtester!</salute></opener>
                
                <p>Besti<choice><abbr>m&#773;</abbr><expan>mm</expan></choice>en Sie uns andere Daten, an denen
                    <lb/>Sie mit v. Zw. ko<choice><abbr>m&#773;</abbr><expan>mm</expan></choice>en kö<choice><abbr>n&#773;</abbr><expan>nn</expan></choice>en. We<choice><abbr>n&#773;</abbr><expan>nn</expan></choice> wir
                    <lb/>Ihren Entschlu<choice><orig>ß</orig><reg>ss</reg></choice> nur etwa 10–12 Tage vor
                    <lb/>dem Konzerte ke<choice><abbr>n&#773;</abbr><expan>nn</expan></choice>en so genügt es! –</p>
                
                <closer>
                    <salute rend="align(center)">Saluti distinti</salute>
                    <signed rend="align(right)"><persName key="E0300125">Huber</persName></signed>
                    <dateline><placeName key="E0500097">Basel</placeName> 11/2</dateline>
                </closer>
                
